snippet.title: Circuit Superstars | Announcement Trailer - E3 2019 | Square Enix Collective | ESRB
snippet.description:
Enter the charming world of motorsport with Circuit Superstars! This dynamic top-down racing game travels through many eras of racing.

Add to your Steam wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1097130/Circuit_Superstars 

Also coming to Xbox One®, PlayStation®4, Nintendo Switch™ in 2020!
